show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/KqGZNZ
show.description: Betrayed by her own blood… Shattered, yet unbroken.. Meera rises from the ashes.! In a world that tried to silence her,  she builds her own empire,  fighting every lie, every betrayal. when destiny brings Priya into her life, the battle between past and future begins.! Witness a woman’s powerful comeback. 'Her Return' - only on Kuku TV.
